title: MFTE 1 Bedroom Coming Soon!
posting_body: ['Welcome Back to School', 'Get to know Jack.', 'Call Now:', 'show contact info', 'x 18', 'Jack Apartments', '1427 11th Ave , Seattle, WA, 98122', 'Visit This Website to See More:', '<URL>', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 565 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Hi, it’s us, Jack.', 'We are the only apartments with high tech units!', 'Including smart home features with Amazon Alexa built in!', 'Full size, smart washer and dryers in all homes!', 'Air-conditioning and heat powered by Mysa smart home thermostat!', 'Secured key fob smart lock entry!', 'Just think of us as this new building that’s been here forever.', 'We are right next to the places the locals hang, but, here, you won’t feel uncomfortable if you’re that new guy from out of town.', 'We’re a fun building with fun amenities, and we’re at the center of everything with something to do every night of the week if you want.', 'You don’t know #Jackapartments—yet.', 'But we hope you decide to come check us out.', 'Features', '- USB outlets.', 'Enough charging space for all your devices and visiting devices from out of town.', '- Built-in closet systems.', "You won't know you need it until you have it.", '- Stylish quartz countertops that impress', '- Vinyl plank flooring.', 'Your pets will love it and so will you.', '- Smart home AC and thermostat powered by Alexa because smarter is always better.', 'Community Amenities', '- Firepits', '- Rooftop Pub', '- Fitness Center', '- Bike Shop', '- BBQ Grills', '- Outdoor TV Lounge', '- DJ Station', '- Social Lounge', '- Living Wall Lounge', '- Rooftop Bark Park', 'Pet Policy', 'We are a pet friendly community: Breed restrictions apply', 'Photos and/or floor plans shown are representational and may not depict the exact layout or features of the available unit.', "If currently occupied, the individual unit you've selected may not be available to tour.", 'Please contact our leasing team with any questions.', 'I5wPR6ROc']
